title: My Gear
description: Here's what tech I'm currently using for coding, videos, and music.

body.raw:
### Laptop 

- Macbook air  2020
- M1/8/256


### Coding

- Editor: VSCode
- Theme: SynthWave '84


### Software

- Spotify
- Telegram
- Discord
